---
title: Creamy Mushroom & Parmesan Gnocchi with Rocket & Pear Salad
description: This mellow combination of buttery mushrooms, fragrant onion and baby spinach, tossed through golden pan-fried gnocchi, makes a meal that's homey and comforting. Served with a tasty rocket and pear salad, it's got the lot!
